name: Jace!
description: '''Jace Lavoer Salter''' (born January 10, 2003), known professionally as '''Iayze''' (pronounced as "Jace") or '''Jace!''', is an American rapper from [[Fort Worth, Texas]]. He is better known for his song "556 (Green Tip)" which received traction on [[TikTok]] due to its quite jaunty, old-fashioned instrumental paired with the modern/violent lyrics that he uses. He is currently independent.
